name: What Comes Between
description:
Walk around from square to square trying to find your goal (yellow cube) while trying not to get stuck from the many obstacles.

I left a lot of bugs in since they actually fit the theme and added to the charm :p 

(also made in 3 hours)

Controls:

WASD to move

Music: 

"Soundscape - D125 by Tri-Tachyon - https://soundcloud.com/tri-tachyon".
from: https://freesound.org/people/Ellary/sounds/319985/
